title: Node_Deep
---
Player: "What's weighing on you the heaviest right now?"

Sofia: "The heaviest thing…"
Sofia: "I think it's the feeling that I'm always performing."
Sofia: "At work, with friends, even with family."
Sofia: "Like there's this version of Sofia everyone expects, and I have to maintain it."

>> media npc type:image unlock:true path:Sofia/CG6

...

Sofia: "But with you? I don't know you well enough to have built that wall yet."
Sofia: "It's freeing. Terrifying. But freeing."

Player: "You don't have to perform here."

Sofia: "Thank you for saying that."
Sofia: "I think I needed to hear it."
Sofia: "Want to know something else?"

>> media npc type:image unlock:true path:Sofia/CG7

...

Sofia: "I took this earlier today."
Sofia: "When I feel overwhelmed, I find quiet spaces. Just to breathe."

<<jump EndNode_Ch2>>

