title: Node_Natural
---
Player: "No pressure. Just say what comes naturally."

Sofia: "Okay… naturally then."
Sofia: "I guess I'll start with something small."
Sofia: "I've been feeling disconnected lately. From everything."
Sofia: "Like I'm going through the motions but not really… present."

>> media npc type:image unlock:true path:Sofia/CG6

...

Sofia: "Does that sound weird?"
Sofia: "I swear I'm not always this melancholic."

Player: "It doesn't sound weird at all."

Sofia: "Good. Because it's been eating at me."
Sofia: "Sometimes I wonder if anyone actually sees me, you know?"
Sofia: "The real me."

>> media npc type:image unlock:true path:Sofia/CG7

...

Sofia: "Sorry, that got heavier than I planned."
Sofia: "But I guess that's the point of having someone to talk to, right?"

